SUMMARY:Science Everywhere (Greensboro)
DESCRIPTION:Visit NCWF Triad Wild Chapter at Science Everywhere on UNC Greensboro’s campus. We will host an interactive exhibit focusing on North Carolina vertebrates and invertebrates. In addition to our exhibit\, Science Everywhere is a free event open to the public that will have dozens of science interactive activities to inspire future scientists of all ages. Learn how science is essential in the life and physical sciences\, arts\, sports\, healthcare\, nursing education and technology! Stop by and say “hi” to some of our ambassador animals! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/science-everywhere-greensboro/
CATEGORIES:Featured
END:VEVENT
