SUMMARY:Earth Day with Kids In Nature Day (Matthews)
DESCRIPTION:Come out to Squirrel Lake Park and celebrate Earth Day with Kids In Nature Day. This event is presented by HAWK and Great Outdoors University. The day will be filled with eco-friendly exhibits and vendors\, hikes and scavenger hunts\, nature crafts STEM activities\, and more! We look forward to seeing you\, your family and friends at Squirrel Lake Park. Kids and adults of ALL AGES are welcome to attend! \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/earth-day-with-kids-in-nature-day-matthews/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/EarthDayWithKIND.jpg
